# 中国地方政府通过“自卖自买”虚增财政收入 (Free Version)

Author: Rebecca Feng / Cao Li

Publisher: 华尔街日报中文网

Published Time: 2023-06-28T07:10:00.000Z

Modified Time: 2023-06-28T07:10:00.000Z

